Localization.Name: XS-90 Explorer Goggles
Localization.Description: With a sleek design suitable for all face shapes, the XS-98 Explorer goggles ensure a fog-free view in any climate, and come with a patented coating that offers strong UV-protection and cuts down on unwanted glare.
